 <br>
               Happy Holidays! <br>
               Terri Bishop<br>
               Acting Human Resources Director <p><hr><center>Now for wrath! <BR>Now for ruin!<BR> And the red dawn!</center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=raeya>Raeya</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/9/03 7:02 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm9.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2192.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.angelfire.com/vamp/raeya/images/pic003.JPG WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re:   OFFICE CHRISTMAS PARTY</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :rollin --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/roll.gif ALT=":rollin"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
